  %h2 What is this?
  %p Poker Signup is a simple way to sign up for upcoming poker games and see who else is playing. To keep it as easy as possible, all you need is a known email address to log in. No need to remember yet another password for a website. Signing up for a game is just a matter of clicking a button and then a final email will be sent out to everyone who is "in" with directions. If a game reaches capacity, a waiting list is created.
  %h2 Why?
  %p
    :markdown
      After announcing a game, I frequently get emails like *"Who is playing so far?"* and *"How many spots left?"*. Here's the answer. It was also a chance to learn [Ruby](http://www.ruby-lang.org)
